In England, in the seven days to 24 October, there were 264,620 new confirmed cases (467.9 new cases per 100,000). There is no change in cases compared to those confirmed in the previous week (seven days to 17 October). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 29 October is 7,633,950 (13,499.4 cases per 100,000 population).
